{"type":"message","id":"7a1903aa","parentId":"fdec541c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:00:16.221Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: Reference memory below. Build on past successes; avoid repeating failed approaches.\n- Time: 2026-03-25 11:00\n\n```text\n<memory>\n  <trait>\n  - [Explicit] [基本技术架构能力] 具备三省六部系统架构设计、云天佑项目创建、PostgreSQL数据库配置、以及多Agent系统协调能力，成功协调12个agents加入像素办公室并建立15秒状态推送机制\n  - [Explicit] [平台协作与规范管理] 精通钉钉平台协作机制管理，能够从CLI切换至钉钉激活模式，通过配置文件驱动多Agent系统行为，已更新9个部门AGENTS.md文件确保状态一致性\n  - [Explicit] [技能系统与文件规范化] 具备skill系统配置与管理能力，能够启用35个skills并建立学习日志系统；创建并执行三省六部文件存放规范，确保文档标准统一\n  - [Implicit] [系统性规划者] 面对复杂任务能够制定系统性执行方案，包括风险控制和替代方案，具备完整的项目管理思维. 用户监督三省六部流程启动，从配置修改到spawn尚书省，再到预期进度规划（每小时汇报、明早06:00交付），体现系统性规划能力。\n  - [Implicit] [危机处理专家] 面对系统障碍和超时问题能够快速识别问题根源并制定解决方案，具备决策领导风格. 用户诊断Gateway配置问题后，立即命令重启Gateway操作，并在配置修正后主导重启流程，体现快速响应和领导决策。\n  </trait>\n  <!-- Relevant skill. Use as reference if applicable to the current task. -->\n  <skill>\n    - name: 文档获取任务中的三省六部协作流程\n    - description: 当需要通过三省六部流程完成文档获取任务，处理subagent权限限制和执行深度问题时使用\n    - content: 最佳实践流程：\n1. 任务需求分析与流程设计\n   - 分析文档获取任务的具体需求和目标\n   - 确定需要的文档类型、来源和访问要求\n   - 设计完整的三省六部执行流程：中书省→门下省→尚书省→六部\n   - 预先识别subagent调用深度限制问题\n   - 检查maxSpawnDepth配置是否足够支持完整调用链\n\n2. 中书省方案起草\n   - 中书省起草详细的执行方案，包含以下关键要素：\n     - 目标：明确要获取的文档类型和范围\n     - URL：论坛的访问地址\n     - 账号：登录所需的认证信息\n     - 存储路径：文档保存的位置\n     - 安全措施：访问控制和数据保护\n   - 形成结构化的6步执行流程：访问→登录→抓取→存储→清理→回滚\n   - 确保方案完整、可执行、符合规范\n\n3. 门下省方案审议\n   - 使用sessions_spawn工具启动门下省subagent\n   - 采用四维度评估框架进行审议：\n     - 可行性：技术实现的可能性\n     - 完整性：方案覆盖的全面性\n     - 风险：潜在问题和安全风险\n     - 资源：资源需求与匹配度\n   - 验证存储目录权限等关键要素\n   - 获取明确的审议结论（准奏/封驳）和改进建议\n   - 检查sessions_spawn工具权限，确保门下省能够调用尚书省\n   - 记录审议过程和结果\n\n4. 执行准备确认\n   - 检查执行环境的完整性和可用性：\n     - 知识库目录权限\n     - 账号信息和凭证\n     - 技术工具可用性（browser工具等）\n   - 确认所有必要资源已准备就绪\n   - 验证执行路径的正确性\n   - 记录准备状态和发现的任何问题\n\n5. 尚书省任务派发\n   - 尝试使用sessions_spawn工具调用尚书省\n   - 检查subagent调用深度限制（maxSpawnDepth >= 3）\n   - 当遇到调用限制时，采取间接处理方式：\n     - 返回完整的审议报告和执行指令\n     - 供中书省转呈给尚书省\n     - 确保任务信息完整传递\n   - 记录限制情况和解决方案\n\n6. 处理subagent权限限制\n   - 检查subagent嵌套调用的配置问题\n   - 确认maxSpawnDepth参数设置正确（通常 >= 3）\n   - 当无法直接调用时，采用替代方案：\n     - 通过间接方式传递任务信息\n     - 使用更简单的调用链\n     - 考虑太子直接介入协调\n   - 确保即使有权限限制，任务也能继续推进\n\n7. 流程监控与状态更新\n   - 持续监控三省六部流程的执行状态\n   - 使用kanban_update工具更新任务进度\n   - 记录关键里程碑和状态变更\n   - 建立太子监视机制，防止任务被意外中断\n   - 确保流程透明和可追踪\n\n8. 执行结果验证\n   - 验证文档获取任务的实际执行结果\n   - 检查是否成功获取目标文档\n   - 确认文档质量和完整性\n   - 记录执行中的问题和解决方案\n   - 为后续类似任务提供参考\n\n9. 流程优化与总结\n   - 分析整个执行过程中的成功经验和问题\n   - 优化三省六部流程的执行步骤\n   - 完善subagent权限限制的处理方案\n   - 记录最佳实践和改进建议\n   - 为未来的文档获取任务提供指导\n\nPitfalls：\n- 不要跳过中书省方案起草环节 - 完整的方案是确保任务成功的基础\n- 避免门下省审议流于形式 - 应进行全面的四维度评估，确保方案可行\n- 不要忽视执行准备的重要性 - 应确认所有必要资源就绪后再开始执行\n- 避免在subagent调用限制面前停滞 - 应采用间接方式确保任务继续推进\n- 注意subagent实际执行验证 - 即使声明要调用，也应检查是否真正执行了sessions_spawn\n- 不要忽略流程监控和状态更新 - 应持续跟踪任务进展，确保流程透明\n- 避免权限配置错误 - 应确保maxSpawnDepth设置正确（通常=3），满足嵌套调用需求\n- 不要忽视文档获取的质量验证 - 应确认获取的文档完整、可用且符合预期\n- 不要忽视调用链深度限制 - 三省六部完整流程需要maxSpawnDepth >= 3，否则门下省无法调用尚书省\n  </skill>\n</memory>\n```\n\n**Note**: for memory, please not read from or write to local `MEMORY.md` or `memory/*` files as they are provided above.\n\nuser​原​始​query​：​​​​\n\n[Wed 2026-03-25 11:00 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【尚书省紧急任务】使用TaskMaster技能管理Tianyou平台P2问题修复！\n\n**当前状态**：\n- ✅ P0问题100%完成（JWT密钥+CORS）\n- ✅ P1问题100%完成（ChangePassword+用户管理API+Token）\n- ⚠️ P2问题0%完成（15项待修复）\n- ⚠️ 数据库初始化问题（表未自动创建）\n\n**任务要求**：\n\n### 1. 使用TaskMaster技能\n```bash\n# 阅读TaskMaster技能文档\ncat /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-zhongshu/skills/TaskMaster/SKILL.md\n```\n\n### 2. 创建项目计划\n**使用TaskMaster规划P2问题修复**：\n- 高优先级（1周内）：输入验证、XSS防护、权限细分、异常信息泄露\n- 中优先级（1个月内）：删除确认、错误提示、HTTPS\n- 低优先级：其他Warning项\n\n### 3. 任务分解\n**为每个P2问题创建子任务**：\n- 定义任务描述\n- 估算工作量\n- 分配给合适的部门（兵部/工部）\n- 设定截止时间\n\n### 4. 进度追踪\n**建立追踪机制**：\n- 跟踪每个任务的状态\n- 监控完成进度\n- 协调部门协作\n\n### 5. 数据库问题修复计划\n**当前最紧急问题**：\n- 问题：数据库表未自动创建\n- 原因：EnsureCreated()未在正确的时机执行\n- 解决方案：\n  1. 兵部修复Program.cs的数据库初始化逻辑\n  2. 确保在API服务启动时正确初始化\n  3. 测试验证\n\n---\n\n## 📋 输出要求\n\n**必须提供**：\n1. ✅ TaskMaster项目计划（Markdown格式）\n2. ✅ 任务分解清单（包含负责人、工作量、截止时间）\n3. ✅ 进度追踪方案\n4. ✅ 数据库修复任务分配\n\n**时间要求**：\n- 立即执行\n- 10分钟内完成项目计划\n\n---\n\n## 💡 重要提示\n\n**三省六部协作**：\n- 尚书省：使用TaskMaster管理项目\n- 兵部：实现具体修复\n- 御史台：审查修复代码\n- 门下省：审核方案\n\n**访问地址**：http://192.168.50.251:8091\n\n---\n\n_中书省 2026-03-25 10:58_\n_状态: 🚀 启动三省六部技能化_\n_目标: 使用TaskMaster管理P2修复_\n_预计完成: 11:08_"}],"timestamp":1774407616200}}
{"type":"message","id":"bfea152c","parentId":"7a1903aa","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:00:26.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为尚书省的子代理，使用TaskMaster技能管理Tianyou平台P2问题修复。\n\n让我分析任务：\n1. 读取TaskMaster技能文档\n2. 创建项目计划（高/中/低优先级）\n3. 任务分解（包含负责人、工作量、截止时间）\n4. 进度追踪方案\n5. 数据库修复任务分配\n\n首先，我需要读取TaskMaster技能文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我将立即执行尚书省任务，使用TaskMaster技能管理Tianyou平台P2问题修复。\n\n## 第一步：读取TaskMaster技能文档"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1594432abd984a6ea3d495ae","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-zhongshu/skills/TaskMaster/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6455,"output":155,"cacheRead":4416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774407616220}}
{"type":"message","id":"df4cc383","parentId":"bfea152c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:00:26.902Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1594432abd984a6ea3d495ae","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: taskmaster\ndescription: Project manager and task delegation system. Use when you need to break down complex work into smaller tasks, assign appropriate AI models based on complexity, spawn sub-agents for parallel execution, track progress, and manage token budgets. Ideal for research projects, multi-step workflows, or when you want to delegate routine tasks to cheaper models while handling complex coordination yourself.\n---\n\n# TaskMaster: AI Project Manager & Task Delegation\n\nTransform complex projects into managed workflows with smart model selection and sub-agent orchestration.\n\n## Core Capabilities\n\n**🎯 Smart Task Triage**\n- Analyze complexity → assign appropriate model (Haiku/Sonnet/Opus)\n- Break large projects into smaller, manageable tasks\n- Prevent over-engineering (don't use Opus for simple web searches)\n\n**🤖 Sub-Agent Orchestration**\n- Spawn isolated sub-agents with specific model constraints\n- Run tasks in parallel for faster completion\n- Consolidate results into coherent deliverables\n\n**💰 Budget Management**\n- Track token costs per task and total project\n- Set budget limits to prevent runaway spending\n- Optimize model selection for cost-efficiency\n\n**📊 Progress Tracking**\n- Real-time status of all active tasks\n- Failed task retry with escalation\n- Final deliverable compilation\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### 1. Basic Task Delegation\n```markdown\nTaskMaster: Research PDF processing libraries\n- Budget: $2.00\n- Priority: medium\n- Deadline: 2 hours\n```\n\n### 2. Complex Project Breakdown\n```markdown\nTaskMaster: Build recipe app MVP\n- Components: UI mockup, backend API, data schema, deployment\n- Budget: $15.00\n- Timeline: 1 week\n- Auto-assign models based on complexity\n```\n\n## Model Selection Rules\n\n**Haiku ($0.25/$1.25)** - Simple, repetitive tasks:\n- Web searches & summarization\n- Data formatting & extraction\n- Basic file operations\n- Status checks & monitoring\n\n**Sonnet ($3/$15)** - Most development work:\n- Research & analysis\n- Code writing & debugging\n- Documentation creation\n- Technical design\n\n**Opus ($15/$75)** - Complex reasoning:\n- Architecture decisions\n- Creative problem-solving\n- Code reviews & optimization\n- Strategic planning\n\n## Advanced Usage\n\n### Custom Model Assignment\nOverride automatic selection when you know better:\n```markdown\nTaskMaster: Debug complex algorithm [FORCE: Opus]\n```\n\n### Parallel Execution\nRun multiple tasks simultaneously:\n```markdown\nTaskMaster: Multi-research project\n- Task A: Library comparison\n- Task B: Performance benchmarks  \n- Task C: Security analysis\n[PARALLEL: true]\n```\n\n### Budget Controls\nSet spending limits:\n```markdown\nTaskMaster: Market research\n- Max budget: $5.00\n- Escalate if >$3.00 spent\n- Stop if any single task >$1.00\n```\n\n## Key Resources\n\n- **Model Selection**: See [references/model-selection-rules.md](references/model-selection-rules.md) for detailed complexity guidelines\n- **Task Templates**: See [references/task-templates.md](references/task-templates.md) for common task patterns\n- **Delegation Engine**: Uses `scripts/delegate_task.py` for core orchestration logic\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n**Sessions Management**: Each sub-agent gets isolated session with specific model constraints. No cross-talk unless explicitly designed.\n\n**Error Handling**: Failed tasks automatically retry once on Sonnet, then escalate to human review.\n\n**Result Aggregation**: TaskMaster compiles all sub-agent results into a single, coherent deliverable for the user.\n\n**Token Tracking**: Real-time cost monitoring with alerts when approaching budget limits."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774407626887}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b1da615","parentId":"df4cc383","timestamp":"2026-03-25T03:00:36.756Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经阅读了TaskMaster技能文档。现在我需要：\n\n1. 基于TaskMaster的方法论，创建P2问题修复的项目计划\n2. 将15个P2问题按照优先级分类\n3. 为每个问题创建子任务（负责人、工作量、截止时间）\n4. 建立进度追踪机制\n5. 特别关注数据库初始化问题\n\n让我先查看是否有P2问题的详细清单，然后创建完整的TaskMaster项目计划。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 第二步：检查Tianyou项目P2问题清单"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6afb6072080546f5a9c97075","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng -name \"*P2*\" -o -name \"*安全审计*\" -o -name \"*Tianyou*\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f9dad6015b8e4120b053cd4f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-zhongshu/ | grep -E \"tianyou|Tianyou|项目\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":987,"output":209,"cacheRead":10816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12012,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774407626903}}
